
# Fibonatix 
![fibonatix](https://static.openfintech.io/vendors/fibonatix/logo.png?w=400&c=v0.59.26#w200)  

## General 
 
**Code:** `fibonatix` 
 
**Name:** 
 
:	[EN] Fibonatix 
 
**Status:** `active` 
 
**Description:** 
 
: [EN]  Payments are a vital part of any successful business An incredible product, with insatiable demand, even at the perfect price point, is worthless without a perfect payment solution. Fibonatix specializes in providing perfect solutions for online business from all around the world. Initially a consultancy, in 2013 we evolved to become a payment services provider offering an unparalleled customer experience to a wide variety of industries worldwide. Much like our name, our history is a sequence of ever-increasing numbers the success of which can be measured by our consistently growing client portfolio, processing volumes, and partners.
